question: What's the weight difference of patient 10038999's body measured at 2100-06-07 05:00:00 compared to the value measured at 2100-06-06 06:00:00?
true_query: SELECT ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10038999 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'daily weight' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) AND chartevents.charttime = '2100-06-07 05:00:00' ) - ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10038999 ) ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'daily weight' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) AND chartevents.charttime = '2100-06-06 06:00:00' )
gen_query: SELECT (chartevents2.valuenum - chartevents1.valuenum) AS weight_difference FROM chartevents chartevents1 JOIN chartevents chartevents2 ON chartevents1.subject_id = chartevents2.subject_id WHERE chartevents1.itemid = (SELECT itemid FROM d_items WHERE label = 'daily weight' AND linksto = 'chartevents') AND chartevents1.subject_id = (SELECT subject_id FROM patient WHERE patient_id = 10038999) AND chartevents1.charttime >= '2021-06-06 06:00:00' AND chartevents2.charttime <= '2021-06-07 05:00:00';

question: What are three of the most frequent specimens taken since 1 year ago?
true_query: SELECT T1.spec_type_desc FROM ( SELECT microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM microbiologyevents WHERE datetime(microbiologyevents.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') GROUP BY microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc ) AS T1 WHERE T1.C1 <= 3
gen_query: SELECT item1, item2, item3 FROM items ORDER BY priority

question: Was the hematocrit reading for patient 10001725 second measured on the last hospital visit less than the first value measured on the last hospital visit?
true_query: SELECT ( SELECT labevents.valuenum FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10001725 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'hematocrit' ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 ) < ( SELECT labevents.valuenum FROM labevents WHERE labevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10001725 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) AND labevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_labitems.itemid FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.label = 'hematocrit' ) ORDER BY labevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1 )
gen_query: WITH last_visit AS ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10001725 ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) , hematocrit_readings AS ( SELECT labevents.charttime, labevents.valuenum, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY labevents.hadm_id ORDER BY labevents.charttime) AS rn FROM labevents JOIN last_visit ON labevents.hadm_id = last_visit.hadm_id JOIN d_labitems ON labevents.itemid = d_labitems.itemid WHERE d_labitems.label = 'hematocrit' ) SELECT hematocrit_readings.valuenum < LAG(hematocrit_readings.valuenum) OVER (PARTITION BY hematocrit_readings.hadm_id ORDER BY hematocrit_readings.charttime) FROM hematocrit_readings WHERE hematocrit_readings.rn = 2

question: What was the duration of the circumcision procedure for patient 3277?
gen_query: SELECT procedures_icd.valuenum FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 3277) AND procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'circumcision' ) ORDER BY procedures_icd.charttime DESC LIMIT 1

question: Has patient 10005909 been diagnosed with any diseases since 2100?
true_query: SELECT COUNT(*)>0 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10005909 ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100'
gen_query: SELECT COUNT(*)>0 FROM diagnoses_icd WHERE diagnoses_icd.subject_id = 10005909 AND diagnoses_icd.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.admittime >= '2100-01-01' )
